        |Deltaf i| ≤ householderQRRhsPanelBackwardBound fp (n + k) n A f) ∧
      (∀ i j, |DeltaR1 i j| ≤ gamma fp n * |R i j|) ∧
      (∀ i j, |DeltaR2 i j| ≤ gamma fp n * |R i j|) ∧
