  simpa [qrLeadingBlock] using hzero

/-- The stored recurrence and signed-alpha nonbreakdown budget supply the
    previous diagonal entries in each displayed leading block.

    Compared with
    `StoredQRSourceOffDiagonalControl.of_stored_trailing_sequence_diag_offdiag_product`,
